<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_f30f9f604cd9.aspx"><b>东门之墠</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonf30f9f604cd9">
<p>东门之墠，茹藘在阪。其室则迩，其人甚远。<br />东门之栗，有践家室。岂不尔思？子不我即！</p>
